## üìä Baseline Scores

| Agent | Task 1 (Spam) | Task 2 (Hate Speech) | Task 3 (Misinfo) | Average |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Random agent** | ~0.31 | ~0.28 | ~0.26 | ~0.28 |
| **Rule-based baseline** | ~0.85 | ~0.72 | ~0.61 | ~0.73 |
| **Target (to beat)** | 0.80 | 0.70 | 0.60 | ‚Äî |

